'''''The Complete History of Corvis Minor''''' was a [[Datacard/Legends|datacard]] volume on the history of [[Corvis Minor]]. One copy of the volume was located on every level of the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]], containing an emergency [[Hold-out blaster/Legends|hold-out blaster]] as opposed to an actual datacard.

